  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Represents a stream for downloading file content from an AI service.
            </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>
            This abstract class extends <see cref="T:System.IO.Stream" /> to provide additional metadata
            about the downloaded file, such as its media type and file name. Implementations
            should override the abstract <see cref="T:System.IO.Stream" /> members and optionally override
            <see cref="P:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.HostedFileDownloadStream.MediaType" /> and <see cref="P:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.HostedFileDownloadStream.FileName" /> to provide file metadata.
            </para>
      <para>
            The <see cref="M:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.HostedFileDownloadStream.ToDataContentAsync(System.Threading.CancellationToken)" /> method provides a convenient way to buffer
            the entire stream content into a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.DataContent" /> instance.
            </para>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
